            <title>[SOLR-4854] Query elevation [elevated] field always false with java binary communication</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4854</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With XMLResponseParser there is no problem, but with default BinaryResponseWriter &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;elevated&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; is always false.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;tomcat 6.0.33, java 1.6.0_26_x64, solrj 4.3&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
